title: Newtown Social Club Hotel
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Same operators as Melbourne's Corner Hotel and Northcote Social Club, this is a bar with pub food menu. Mostly pizza with a couple of vegan items marked, one faux dog that's a house-made spiced tofu sausage with sauerkraut and tomato chilli jam.
